            "id": "4542731",
            "title": "Runway Growth Finance announces notes offering",
            "description": "<html><body><ul>\n<li><span>Runway Growth Finance (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/RWAY\" title=\"Runway Growth Finance Corp.\">RWAY</a></span>) <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/pr/20376580-runway-growth-finance-corp-commences-offering-of-notes\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"commenced\">commenced</a> an underwritten offering of unsecured notes to be listed on the Nasdaq Global Select Market.</span></li>\n<li><span>If approved, the trading will potentially start within 30 days of issuance.</span></li>\n<li><span>The interest rates and terms will be set at pricing.</span></li>\n<li><span>Net proceeds will be used to repay outstanding debt—including up to $51.75 million of the company's 8.00% notes due December 2027—finance its prior SWK Holdings acquisition, and support general corporate purposes.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"signup_widget_placeholder\"></div>\n</body></html>",
